        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FLUXO_0000217"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The mathematical representation of a metabolic network, with rows representing metabolites and columns representing reactions. Each value indicates the stoichiometric coefficients, metabolites that are consumed are negative values and produced are positive values.</obo:IAO_0000115>
