        <obo:IAO_0000115>Isomers having the same number of each isotopic atom but differing in their positions. The term is a contraction of &apos;isotopic isomer&apos;.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MSIO_0000036</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
