        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FLUXO_0000049"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>An experiment measures the rate at which isotopically labelled compounds are incorporated into cellular metabolites over time, specifically before the system reaches a stable isotopic equilibrium.</obo:IAO_0000115>
